<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8">
		<title>首页</title>
        <script src="../../Scripts/jquery-3.4.1.js"></script>
        <script src="../../Scripts/echarts.js"></script>
		<script src="../../Source/packages/layui/layui.js"></script>
		<script src="../../Scripts/Project/Home/homePage.js"></script>
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="../../Source/packages/layui/css/layui.css">
	</head>
	<body>
		<fieldset class="layui-elem-field layui-field-title" style="margin-top: 50px;">
            <legend>当前位置&gt;&gt;主页</legend>
        </fieldset>
        <div style="padding:20px; background-color:#F2F2F2;">
            <div class="layui-row layui-col-space15">
                <div class="layui-col-md12">
                    <div class="layui-card">
                        <div class="layui-card-header">
                            快速导航
                        </div>
                        <div class="layui-card-body">
                            <button class="layui-btn" onclick="linkBtn('/Project/Project')">新建评审</button>
                            <button class="layui-btn" onclick="linkBtn('/Expert/Expert')">评委信息</button>
                            <button class="layui-btn" onclick="linkBtn('/Result/Result')">评审结果</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="layui-col-md12">
                    <div class="layui-card">
                        <div class="layui-card-body">
                            <div id="echarts_vote" style="width: 600px;height: 400px;margin:0 auto; text-align: center;"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="layui-col-md12">
                    <div class="layui-card">
                        <div class="layui-card-header">
                            使用教程
                        </div>
                        <div class="layui-card-body">
                            1、新建项目前请先下载项目文件模板，按模板格式录入数据后导入即可
                            <br>
                            2、新建的项目在启动前可修改，若启动项目则无法修改，只能删除
                            <br>
                            3、启动项目后，请发放评委二维码，开始评审
                            <br>
                            4、结束评审并统计结果后，可让评委再次扫码，查看评审结果
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
	</body>
</html>
